OL,3,CMan fighting for his life as two
OL,4,Carrested following van crash
OL,6,FA man is fighting for his life after
OL,7,Fhe was the victim of a hit and run
OL,8,Fwhile out jogging - with police keen
OL,9,Fto identify him "as a matter of
OL,10,Furgency".
OL,12,FThe man, in his 50s, was discovered
OL,13,Fwith serious injuries after emergency
OL,14,Fservices were called to reports he had
OL,15,Fbeen hit by a transit van at around
OL,16,F6.30pm on Sunday, 25 February.
OL,18,FHe was taken to hospital, where his
OL,19,Fcondition is described as critical.
