OL,3,CMan fighting for his life as two
OL,4,Carrested following van crash
OL,6,FThe driver of the silver transit van,
OL,7,Fbelieved to be involved in the crash,
OL,8,Ffailed to stop at the scene, on Utting
OL,9,FAvenue East in Norris Green, .
OL,11,Fofficers later spotted the van,
OL,12,Fbelieved to have been involved in the
OL,13,Fcrash, parked up at the junction of
OL,14,FHollingbourne Place and Hollingbourne
OL,15,FRoad, nearby.
OL,17,FA 24-year-old man from Norris Green
OL,18,Fand a 44-year-old woman from Westvale
OL,19,Fin Kirkby are being questioned on
OL,20,Fsuspicion of causing injury by
OL,21,Fdangerous driving.
