OL,6,FPolice are now appealing to help
OL,7,Fidentify the victim, who was wearing a
OL,8,Fdistinctive yellow cap.
OL,10,FHe is a white male, of slim build,
OL,11,Fwith bald head and clean shaven.
OL,13,FAt the time of the collision, he was
OL,14,Fwearing a black Karrimor long-sleeved
OL,15,Fjacket, a bright yellow Karrimor cap,
OL,16,Fblack gloves and black New Balance
OL,17,Ftrainers with green stripes on the
OL,18,Fside.
