OL,4,Carrested following van crash
OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Jason Higham, from
OL,7,FMerseyside Police Serious Collision
OL,8,FInvestigation Unit (SCIU), said: "We
OL,9,Fare carrying out extensive enquiries
OL,10,Fto identify the pedestrian, but would
OL,11,Furge anyone who think they may know
OL,12,Fhim to please contact us.
OL,14,F"He is in a critical condition, so it
OL,15,Fis crucial that we identify him and
OL,16,Flet his family know as soon as
OL,17,Fpossible.
OL,26,@pD@bOU
