OL,4,Carrested following van crash
OL,6,F"We suspect the man was out exercising
OL,7,Fat the time of the collision and we
OL,8,Fhope his neighbours, family or friends
OL,9,Fwill recognise him due to the sports
OL,10,Fclothing he was wearing."
OL,12,FHe added: "Although we have made two
OL,13,Farrests, we are appealing for those
OL,14,Fwho saw the collision or saw a silver
OL,15,Fvan being driving around the area or
OL,16,Fparked on Hollingbourne Place or
OL,17,FHollingbourne Road with damage to the
OL,18,Ffront of it to please get in touch.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@YO]tD@KOU
