OL,6,F"This collision happened at busy
OL,7,Flocation and as such I believe it
OL,8,Fwould have been witnessed by members
OL,9,Fof the public or they saw the van
OL,10,Fdriving from the scene or being parked
OL,11,Fup.
OL,13,F"In addition, I would ask local
OL,14,Fbusinesses and homeowners with CCTV to
OL,15,Fcheck their systems to see if the
OL,16,Fdamaged van has been captured on it.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
