OL,6,F"Likewise, the area was busy with
OL,7,Ftraffic and as such I would also ask
OL,8,Fanyone who was in the area at the time
OL,9,Fwho has dashcam fitted to their
OL,10,Fvehicles to urgently review it. Any
OL,11,Fhelp we receive, no matter how
OL,12,Finsignificant it may seem can assist
OL,13,Four investigation."
OL,15,FAnyone who witnessed the collision or
OL,16,Fcaptured anything on CCTV or dashcam
OL,17,Fis asked to contact Serious Collision
OL,18,FInvestigation Unit on (0151) 777 5747,
OL,19,For email SCIU@merseyside.police.uk.
